  <h2>About WebNews</h2>
  
  <p>WebNews is a Ruby on Rails frontend for <a href="https://wiki.csh.rit.edu/wiki/News">CSH News</a> brought to you by Alex Grant, a.k.a. <a href="https://wiki.csh.rit.edu/wiki/User:Grantovich">Grantovich</a>. Documentation on various features and implementation details is available on the <a href="https://wiki.csh.rit.edu/wiki/WebNews">WebNews wiki page</a>.</p>
  
  <p>The WebNews code lives on <a href="https://github.com/grantovich/CSH-WebNews">GitHub</a>. Bug reports and feature requests should be submitted to the <a href="https://github.com/grantovich/CSH-WebNews/issues">issue tracker</a>. Developers of CSH apps, scripts, web sites, etc. might be interested in the <a href="https://github.com/grantovich/CSH-WebNews/wiki/API">WebNews API</a>.</p>
  
